    "body": "The option `add_newline` refers to the new line **above** the prompt (see: [Documentation/Configuration/Prompt](https://starship.rs/config/#prompt)).\r\nThe feature you are looking for is `line_break`, which removes the line break inside the prompt  (see: [Documentation/Configuration/Line Break](https://starship.rs/config/#line-break))",
